\pard\plain \s2\qj \b\f16 {Chaotic Magickal Creatures\par 
}\pard\plain \qj \f16\fs20 \tab Certain monstrous species are varieties of Chaos creatures with fairly stable forms and features. As such, they are referred to as \ldblquote Chaos species\rdblquote  rather than as Chaos mutants or as spawn of Chaos. 
Though the dominant characteristics of these chaos species seem to breed true, there is a wide variation in specific features, and a wide variation in the quality of magickal properties of their derivatives.\par 
\tab Chaos species of monsters are typically rare, found only in remote regions, perilous for specimen collectors. As such, their derivatives are frequently scarce and dear.\par 
