\pard\plain \s3\qj \f16 {\fs28 Fugacious Elements} (Spirits and Essences)\par 
\pard\plain \qj \f16\fs20 \tab Fugacious elements are exquisitely pure elemental substances. Spirits are compounded within a neutral fluid matrix, and must be stored and transported in specially designed airtight, securely sealed containers. 
Essences are free, uncompounded, and extremely volatile; as such, they must be stored and transported in enchanted containers.\par 
\tab Type of Reagent: True Elemental\par 
\tab Cost: 2000 GC\par 
\tab Availability: Average\par 
\tab From Scratch: 10 measures of durable element yields 1 measure; process requires 2d10+20 hours.\par 
\tab Examples:\par 
